WEBVTT

NOTE Captions for the ALF (Chapter 2800) persona video. Timings are approximate.

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.500
Running an assisted living facility? Chapter 2800 asks more of you.

2
00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:12.000
Sixteen hours of training a year per direct care worker.

3
00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:19.500
Plus separate dementia hours that don't count toward the sixteen,
special-care-unit requirements, and ASP assessments — each with its own due date.

4
00:00:19.500 --> 00:00:26.000
And those separate dementia hours? That's exactly where
assisted living facilities get cited.

5
00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:32.500
CareBase tracks them apart from the sixteen, so nothing is ever
counted twice, with Chapter 2800 mapped for you.

6
00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:37.500
So you walk into your survey already ready.
